---
title: "Skills — The Agent ↔ Binary Protocol"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as 👤 Developer
    participant Agent as 🤖 Coding Agent
    participant Skill as 📜 Skill File
    participant CX as ⚙️ cx binary
    participant Docs as 📁 docs/
    participant Mem as 🧠 docs/memories/
    participant MCP as 🔌 Linear MCP

    Note over Dev,Mem: Session Start

    Dev->>Agent: "Let's work on the gas alerting feature"

    Agent->>Agent: Spawns primer subagent
    Agent->>Skill: Primer reads cx-prime.md skill
    Skill-->>Agent: "Classify mode, call cx context --mode, distill"
    Agent->>CX: cx context --mode build
    CX->>Docs: Reads specs, memories, changes
    Docs-->>CX: Context map
    CX-->>Agent: Structured map of available context
    Agent->>CX: cx context --load spec gas-monitoring
    CX-->>Agent: Full spec content
    Agent-->>Agent: Primer returns ~600 tokens of distilled context

    Agent->>Skill: Reads cx-change.md skill
    Skill-->>Agent: "To start work, run cx change status"
    Agent->>CX: cx change status
    CX->>Docs: Scan docs/changes/
    Docs-->>CX: Active changes list
    CX-->>Agent: "No existing change for gas alerting"

    Note over Dev,Mem: Brainstorm Phase

    Agent->>Skill: Reads cx-brainstorm.md skill
    Skill-->>Agent: "For new features, run cx brainstorm"
    Agent->>CX: cx brainstorm
    CX->>Docs: Creates masterfile.md template
    CX-->>Agent: Template path + instructions
    Agent->>Docs: Fills masterfile.md with structured intent

    Dev->>Agent: "Also consider the firmware side"
    Agent->>Skill: Reads cx-refine.md skill
    Skill-->>Agent: "Edit masterfile directly, no binary command"
    Agent->>Docs: Edits masterfile.md with new firmware considerations

    Dev->>Agent: "Looks good, let's go"

    Note over Dev,Mem: Decompose Phase

    Agent->>Skill: Reads cx-decompose.md skill
    Agent->>CX: cx decompose
    CX->>Docs: Reads masterfile.md
    CX->>Docs: Creates docs/changes/fix-gas-alerts/<br/>  proposal.md (template)<br/>  design.md (template)<br/>  tasks.md (template)<br/>  specs/gas-monitoring/delta.md
    CX->>Docs: Archives masterfile → docs/archive/
    CX-->>Agent: "Change created. Fill templates."
    Agent->>Docs: Reads docs/specs/gas-monitoring/spec.md
    Agent->>Docs: Fills proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md
    Agent->>Skill: Reads cx-linear.md skill
    Skill-->>Agent: "Create Linear issues via MCP, write refs to tasks.md"
    Agent->>MCP: Create issues: CUB-140, CUB-141, CUB-142
    MCP-->>Agent: Issues created
    Agent->>Docs: Writes Linear refs to tasks.md

    Note over Dev,Mem: Implementation Phase

    Agent->>Docs: Reads tasks.md
    Agent->>Agent: Writes code for task 1
    Agent->>CX: cx memory save --title "Gas threshold uses INT not FLOAT in firmware"
    CX->>Mem: Writes observation .md file

    Agent->>Agent: Writes code for task 2, 3
    Agent->>MCP: Updates Linear issue status via MCP

    Note over Dev,Mem: Archive Phase

    Agent->>CX: cx change archive fix-gas-alerts
    CX->>Docs: Validates all tasks complete
    CX->>Docs: Merges delta.md → specs/gas-monitoring/spec.md
    CX->>Docs: Moves change → docs/archive/
    CX->>Mem: Writes completion summary .md
    CX-->>Agent: "✅ Archived. Specs updated."
